<p>
for the <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/LineSegment.html">line seg=
ment</a> <img src=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/images/equations/GoldenR=
atio/Inline13.svg" class=3D"inlineformula" style=3D"max-height:100%;max-wid=
