</div>
<p>
The golden ratio is given by the <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/S=
eries.html">series</a>
</p>
<div>
<table summary=3D"" width=3D"100%" align=3D"center" cellspacing=3D"0" cellp=
