 style=3D"max-height:100%;max-width:100%" border=3D"0" width=3D"141" height=
=3D"50" alt=3D" phi=3D1+sum_(n=3D1)^infty((-1)^(n+1))/(F_nF_(n+1)). "></td>=
<td align=3D"right" width=3D"3">
<div id=3D"eqn13" class=3D"eqnum">
