</div>
</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
<p>
A representation in terms of a <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/Nes=
tedRadical.html">nested radical</a> is
</p>
<div>
<table summary=3D"" width=3D"100%" align=3D"center" cellspacing=3D"0" cellp=
