tio/Inline37.svg" class=3D"inlineformula" style=3D"max-height:100%;max-widt=
h:100%" border=3D"0" width=3D"100" height=3D"22" alt=3D"lim_(n-&gt;infty)a_=
n=3Dphi">.
</p>
<p>
<img src=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/images/equations/GoldenRatio/Inli=
ne38.svg" class=3D"inlineformula" style=3D"max-height:100%;max-width:100%" =
border=3D"0" width=3D"9" height=3D"21" alt=3D"phi"> is the "worst" real num=
