<p>
(OEIS <a href=3D"http://oeis.org/A000012">A000012</a>; Williams 1979, p.&nb=
sp;52; Steinhaus 1999, p.&nbsp;45; Livio 2002, p.&nbsp;84) has the smallest=
 possible term (1) in each
