athworld.wolfram.com/Convergent.html">convergents</a> <img src=3D"https://m=
athworld.wolfram.com/images/equations/GoldenRatio/Inline45.svg" class=3D"in=
lineformula" style=3D"max-height:100%;max-width:100%" border=3D"0" width=3D=
"82" height=3D"22" alt=3D"x_n=3Dp_n/q_n"> are given by the <a href=3D"https=
://mathworld.wolfram.com/QuadraticRecurrenceEquation.html">quadratic
