<tbody><tr><td align=3D"left"><img src=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/ima=
ges/equations/GoldenRatio/NumberedEquation11.svg" class=3D"numberedequation=
" style=3D"max-height:100%;max-width:100%" border=3D"0" width=3D"99" height=
=3D"42" alt=3D" x_n=3D1+1/(x_(n-1)), "></td><td align=3D"right" width=3D"3"=
>
