</p>
<div>
<table summary=3D"" width=3D"100%" align=3D"center" cellspacing=3D"0" cellp=
adding=3D"0" style=3D"padding-left: 50px">
<tbody><tr><td align=3D"left"><img src=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/ima=
ges/equations/GoldenRatio/NumberedEquation12.svg" class=3D"numberedequation=
" style=3D"max-height:100%;max-width:100%" border=3D"0" width=3D"77" height=
=3D"42" alt=3D" x_n=3D(F_(n+1))/(F_n), "></td><td align=3D"right" width=3D"=
3">
