=3D"0" width=3D"41" height=3D"25" alt=3D"|_nphi^2_|">. This sequence also h=
as many connections with the
 <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/FibonacciNumber.html">Fibonacci n=
umbers</a>. It is plotted above (mod 2)
 as a <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/RecurrencePlot.html">recurre=
nce plot</a>.
</p>
